casebody.data:
Re: Shuja Sayed AHMAD et ux
v.
STATE of Arizona Arizona Supreme Court No. CV-16-0269-PR Supreme Court of Arizona. August 30, 2017 ORDERED: Petition for Review = GRANTED. FURTHER ORDERED: Vacating the Court of Appeals' Opinion and remanding to that court for reconsideration in light of Soto v. Sacco, 242 Ariz. 474 , 398 P.3d 90 (2017). The Clerk of the Court of Appeals, Division One, Phoenix, shall retain the remaining record. Justice Gould did not participate in the determination of this matter.
